{"title":"春庙听鼓","authors":["聪聪"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春庙听鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪聪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大树在笑，小树在舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近处的海浪也在欢呼——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春来了！万里华夏大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在和风中重新复苏……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听到了吗？海外赤子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城如飞龙穿云破雾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋进的鼓，腾飞的鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚咚咚咚震撼着肺腑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是啊，每当春庙聚会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当大地卸冬装换绿服，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡亲们便从四方赶来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼观六路大饱耳福。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让大地的震动驱散寒冷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请鼓槌验看手的力度；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，每擂一鼓、每敲一槌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华大地就播下一成富足。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}